  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n## Description\r\nDepending on how the max value was rounded, it may happen that using the maximum value by clicking on it will result in error (exceeding balance).\r\n\r\nIt's also problematic to send exactly all funds owned by the user.\r\n\r\n[Kazam_screencast_00030.webm](https://github.com/status-im/status-desktop/assets/20650004/a99def80-8503-4cd6-8c79-fb4b9d4eb765)\r\n\r\n## Steps to reproduce\r\n1. Go to wallet\r\n2. Open \"Send\" dialog to send some ETH\r\n3. Click \"Max: xxx ETH\" in the right top corner\r\n4. Depending how the value was rounded, it may result in red amount\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nAfter clicking \"Max: ...\" the value in the input field is valid\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\nAfter clicking \"Max: ...\" the value marked red because of exceeding balance\r\n\r\n\r\n",
